Meet the pillars of wisdom behind DJS ACM SIGAI—our esteemed Faculty Coordinators! Their expertise and dedication are the foundation of our journey into the ever-evolving world of Artificial Intelligence.

Meet the mentors who shape our future:

Dr. Aruna Gawade - DJS ACM SIGAI Convener
Prof. Ragini Mishra - DJS ACM SIGAI Faculty Coordinator

Their expertise and mentorship light the way as we strive to push boundaries and innovate in the world of AI. With their guidance, we’re confident in reaching new heights and making a lasting impact in the AI community.
